SHE WAS TALKING.

04:51.508 --> 04:54.119
SHE SQUASHED HIM.

04:54.119 --> 04:55.512
WHOA!

04:56.905 --> 04:58.428
HER DOG.

04:58.428 --> 05:01.736
NOW ALL I HAVE LEFT
ARE THESE PICTURES.

05:01.736 --> 05:03.433
COME AND SIT.

05:07.437 --> 05:09.265
LOOK AT THIS.

05:09.265 --> 05:11.485
CHESTER ON THE BEACH
IN MENDOCINO.

05:11.485 --> 05:14.836
WASN'T HE THE MOST BEAUTIFUL
DOG YOU'VE EVER SEEN?

05:14.836 --> 05:19.188
HE USED TO LOVE
CHEWING THE WRAPPING OFF
OF OUR CHRISTMAS PRESENTS.

05:19.188 --> 05:23.845
I KNOW I HAVE
A PICTURE SOMEWHERE.

05:23.845 --> 05:25.716
Bailey: YOU TELL ME
WHAT TO BELIEVE!

05:25.716 --> 05:29.154
"OH, BAY, I'M SO CONFUSED
ABOUT COLLEGE

05:29.154 --> 05:31.287
"AND MY FUTURE,
AND MY FOLKS,
THEY NEVER UNDERSTAND.

05:31.287 --> 05:33.594
"BUT YOU GUYS, YOU GUYS
ARE LIKE MY FAMILY.

05:33.594 --> 05:35.117
"SO I'LL JUST
CRASH WITH YOU.

05:35.117 --> 05:37.119
IT'LL BE LIKE OLD TIMES."I FREAKED, OK?

05:37.119 --> 05:38.207
YEAH, YOU'RE
REALLY SOMETHING
UNDER PRESSURE.

05:38.207 --> 05:39.774
HEY, UNTIL YOU'RE THERE,

05:39.774 --> 05:41.166
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'D DO, EITHER!

05:41.166 --> 05:42.429
I WOULDN'T WALK AWAY
FROM A GIRL

05:42.429 --> 05:43.386
WHO TOLD ME
SHE WAS PREGNANT.

05:43.386 --> 05:45.040
SHE NEVER TOLD ME!

05:45.040 --> 05:46.694
I HEARD THE WHOLE THING
FROM A FRAT GUY

05:46.694 --> 05:48.478
WHO WAS A FRIEND
OF A FRIEND OF HERS.

05:48.478 --> 05:50.045
SO?

05:50.045 --> 05:52.656
SO I FIGURED SHE'D
GET IT TAKEN CARE OF.

05:52.656 --> 05:54.919
THAT SHE WAS EMBARRASSED,
THAT SHE DIDN'T WANT
TO TALK TO ME,

05:54.919 --> 05:57.052
AND SHE'D GET IT
TAKEN CARE OF WHILE I WAS
OUT HERE WITH YOU!

05:57.052 --> 05:59.010
SHE CALLED YOU, WILL!

05:59.010 --> 06:00.447
YOU WOULDN'T
TALK TO HER!

06:02.666 --> 06:04.451
THE GIRL FOLLOWED YOU
ACROSS THE COUNTRY!

06:04.451 --> 06:07.671
YEAH! AND THAT'S WEIRD, OK?

06:07.671 --> 06:10.500
I MEAN, YOU MEET SOMEONE
FROM ANOTHER SCHOOL
AT A FRAT PARTY,

06:10.500 --> 06:12.023
YOU TALK TO THEM
FOR, LIKE, AN HOUR,

06:12.023 --> 06:14.243
YOU GET SMASHED,
YOU GO SOMEPLACE AND DO IT,

06:14.243 --> 06:16.245
YOU DON'T EXACTLY
EXPECT TO SETTLE DOWN

06:16.245 --> 06:17.768
AND RAISE A FAMILY WITH THEM!

06:17.768 --> 06:18.856
[DOOR OPENING]

06:21.946 --> 06:22.860
HEY.

06:24.558 --> 06:26.429
WHAT'S GOING ON?

06:26.429 --> 06:28.779
CHANGE OF PLANS
IS WHAT'S GOING ON.

06:28.779 --> 06:31.391
SO IF WILL HAS TO STAY
AT SOME FLEABAG MOTEL,
THEN, YOU KNOW WHAT?

06:31.391 --> 06:33.915
THAT'S FINE. BE MY GUEST,
BUT SHE'S PREGNANT,

06:33.915 --> 06:36.613
SHE'S A THOUSAND MILES
AWAY FROM HOME,
AND SHE'S STAYING HERE.

06:36.613 --> 06:38.310
NO DISCUSSION.

07:09.603 --> 07:11.909
OH...CHARLIE?

07:15.043 --> 07:16.305
CHARLIE!

07:16.305 --> 07:18.612
Charlie: DAPHNE?COME QUICK!

07:18.612 --> 07:20.091
WHAT'S GOING ON?
WHAT HAPPENED?

07:20.091 --> 07:22.050
SOMETHING'S WRONG.

07:22.050 --> 07:24.618
I'M SEEING, LIKE, SPOTS,
AND EVERYTHING'S-- AND I CAN'T--

07:24.618 --> 07:26.794
WELL, MAYBE YOUR EYES
ARE JUST ADJUSTING--NO, NO, NO!

07:26.794 --> 07:29.274
SOMETHING IN MY HEAD,
IT'S BAD,

07:29.274 --> 07:31.233
AND EVERYTHING'S,
LIKE, I CAN'T--

07:31.233 --> 07:32.234
I FEEL LIKE
I'M GONNA PASS OUT.

07:32.234 --> 07:33.801
WHOA. HEY.

07:33.801 --> 07:34.976
CALL THE DOCTOR,
CHARLIE!

07:34.976 --> 07:36.543
SOMETHING'S WRONG!

07:36.543 --> 07:38.153
SHE'S 27 YEARS OLD,
IN HER 32nd WEEK...

07:38.153 --> 07:39.720
IT'S GONNA BE OK.

07:39.720 --> 07:42.113
Nurse: 116 OVER 110.
PROTEIN COUNT'S 38,000.

07:42.113 --> 07:43.375
SHE'S PRESENTING AS
SEVERELY PREECLAMPTIC...

07:43.375 --> 07:44.376
DON'T LEAVE, CHARLIE!

07:44.376 --> 07:46.117
I'M RIGHT HERE.

07:46.117 --> 07:47.423
NO. I'M RIGHT HERE.
YOU CAN'T LEAVE THIS ROOM.

07:47.423 --> 07:48.511
OH, GOD.
OH, PLEASE STAY HERE.

07:48.511 --> 07:49.860
I'M RIGHT HERE.

07:49.860 --> 07:51.253
I'M RIGHT HERE.
DON'T GO, OK?

07:51.253 --> 07:52.167
I'M RIGHT HERE.

07:56.606 --> 07:59.043
I DON'T KNOW, BAY.
NO. I NEED YOU TO--

07:59.043 --> 08:03.265
OK. OK, JUST CALL JULIA
AND GET HER TO STAY
WITH OWEN.

08:03.265 --> 08:04.919
RIGHT.

08:04.919 --> 08:06.224
OK.

08:06.224 --> 08:07.661
THANKS.

08:09.706 --> 08:12.100
THAT WAS BAILEY.
HE'S GONNA COME RIGHT OVER.

08:12.100 --> 08:14.450
OW!

08:14.450 --> 08:16.713
THAT REALLY HURT.

08:16.713 --> 08:18.976
WHAT--WHAT HURTS?
WHAT'S WRONG?

08:18.976 --> 08:21.979
SHE HAS SOME PAIN
IN HER UPPER ABDOMEN.

08:21.979 --> 08:23.764
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

08:23.764 --> 08:26.331
THAT'S A FURTHER INDICATION
OF LIVER INVOLVEMENT.

08:27.724 --> 08:29.073
OH.

08:29.073 --> 08:30.379
THAT'S WHY
YOU'RE FEELING

08:30.379 --> 08:32.207
SOME OF THE THINGS
YOU'RE FEELING--

08:32.207 --> 08:35.645
THE PAIN,
THE WEIRD REFLEXES,
THE VISION PROBLEMS.

08:35.645 --> 08:37.342
FROM YOUR
BLOOD PRESSURE,

08:37.342 --> 08:39.693
A SWOLLEN LIVER,
SOME SWELLING IN YOUR BRAIN

08:39.693 --> 08:41.651
THAT COMES
ALONG WITH IT.

08:41.651 --> 08:45.263
SO WE WILL
WATCH YOUR NUMBERS,
WE'LL MONITOR THE BABY,

08:45.263 --> 08:46.830
AND IF YOU GET
IN TROUBLE,

08:46.830 --> 08:48.266
YOU'RE ALREADY
IN THE HOSPITAL,

08:48.266 --> 08:52.183
SO WE'LL BE ABLE
TO ACT IMMEDIATELY.

08:52.183 --> 08:54.795
CLAUD--CLAUD, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HER EXACT CONDITION IS.

08:54.795 --> 08:56.144
I JUST WALKED IN THE DOOR.

08:56.144 --> 08:58.233
PUT THE ORANGE JUICE
DOWN, OWEN.

08:58.233 --> 09:00.191
WOULD YOU WATCH HIM
FOR A SECOND?

09:00.191 --> 09:02.237
NO. I TALKED TO CHARLIE
FOR, LIKE, A MINUTE

09:02.237 --> 09:04.239
BEFORE I CAME OVER HERE
TO WATCH OWEN.

09:04.239 --> 09:05.370
I COULD HAVE
DONE THAT FOR YOU.

09:05.370 --> 09:07.111
THAT'S NOT YOUR JOB.

09:07.111 --> 09:08.983
LISTEN, I'LL TRY
TO REACH THEM AT--

09:08.983 --> 09:10.288
AT THE HOSPITAL, AND THEN
I'LL CALL YOU BACK, OK?

09:10.288 --> 09:12.290
IT SOUNDS
REALLY SCARY, JULE.

09:12.290 --> 09:14.466
I FEEL LIKE I SHOULD
BE HOME WITH YOU GUYS.

09:14.466 --> 09:16.947
NO. JUST STAY THERE,
AND I'LL CALL YOU RIGHT BACK--

09:16.947 --> 09:18.949
OWEN, PUT THE MARSHMALLOW
FLUFF DOWN.
I'M HUNGRY.

09:18.949 --> 09:21.212
I CAN'T JUST SIT HERE.WE'RE ALL SITTING HERE.

09:21.212 --> 09:24.259
I'M STUCK IN THE HOUSE,
CLAUD--OWEN!

09:24.259 --> 09:26.217
WOULD YOU GET HIM
OUT OF HERE?

09:26.217 --> 09:28.045
LET'S GO, BUDDY.

09:28.045 --> 09:31.135
JUST SIT TIGHT,
AND I'LL CALL YOU BACK,
ALL RIGHT?

09:37.794 --> 09:39.361
GLOBAL AIRLINES, PLEASE.

09:41.493 --> 09:44.061
OH, I--

09:44.061 --> 09:45.759
